{
  "stem": "3346.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Jewish director and his wife and their-- I think they were their assistants or whatever-- tried to escape, and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They got caught, obviously, and shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember that we had to-- we spent the whole day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to-- their bodies were thrown there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to-- the whole camp had to walk by and look at them, just, you know, to see what would happen to any one of us if we escaped, I assume.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I guess, you know, it's, it's many days, and, and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And some days, an awful lot of things happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the other days, nothing happened at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then it has been 50, 50 years, and it's sort of tough to remember after 50 years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You remember the most vivid detail, details, but not the be every day things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- while there were children in Plaszow, I did-- my cousins were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were other children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Play?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, you may call it play, but very peculiar games.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think mainly escapists games.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't mean trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But escapism, mental escapism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Going-- sort of children dream things up anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well we did a little more than that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We tried to, I guess, just disappear mentally from there as, as often as we could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow, it wasn't too bad, or at least it was sufficient.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Black bread, marmalade, potato soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You-- we didn't starve, not in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not the children, at least.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know about the grown-ups, but the children definitely not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, thank God.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember the-- there were-- all of them walked around with big dogs, especially when there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
